item.title: K3RA forming new Tech Class on Zoom
item.author: admin@w3cwc.com (Antietam Radio Association)
item.description: Roland Anders, K3RA, is starting up a Technician Class for those new hams who would rather join a class than to self-study. This class will be on Zoom. This is not an Antietam Radio class, but we fully support his efforts, and are posting his class to better the entire ham community.
